===

Each of us were given a challenge. A new experience awaited the six of us, calling for our undivided attention. So, what did this entail? In short, we were asked to learn a song and film it all in one take – live filming. 

Through this adventure, we discovered the importance of teamwork. In the process of filming, not only did we receive the satisfaction of finally completing a good take, we also formed new bonds with one another. Between takes, uncontrollable laughter was not uncommon. Each of us struggled to maintain our composure as Nick gracefully tripped over wires in order to gain a more epic shot. 

With the project reaching completion, we each gained a valuable experience, as well as valuable friendships. 

I hope you're blessed by watching this video as much as we were making it.

May Jesus be your all in all, every day.

— Tessa, Fountainview Student


===

Fountainview Academy is a Christian high school based in southern British Columbia, Canada, which holds Province of BC Ministry of Education accreditation. Students from all over the world are attracted to Fountainview because of its balanced approach to education. Each staff member is personally committed to the eternal success of every student, and together they strive for the highest standards in every respect.
